Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:33.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:48.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:59.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:02.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,130.389)}Monstrous Inokabuton,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(751,500)}Defeat \NKamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(535,715)}With Insanity Gas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:36.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\c&H0D0805&\3c&H172A33&}Keiyo Penitentiary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will... I will crawl my way out of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and murder all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your call...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to crawl your way\Nout of hell and murder those men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching for a man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the man\Nwe've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We must modify him, set him loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn Tokyo into\Na city of corpses at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. What are you going to do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We saved you from execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd best do as we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,These men are going to transfer\Nyour brain to another body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a powerful rival\Nfor the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H0D0805&}Murayama Zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's gonna be dawn soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better set things up fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, our animals do like\Nan early breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say no to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- See ya!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kawasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the boars got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It got out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they breathed out some yellow\Npowder and they were both passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yellow powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The forensics lab is\Ninvestigating now, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But they said it had an\Noppressively bad smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the boar that broke\Nout of its cage and escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't leave any tracks, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it vanished into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. Animals don't just vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But a boar went missing, and the\Ncaretakers were found unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a connection there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, where are the caretakers now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They were admitted to a\Nhospital close to the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Going to visit?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Taki's not here,\Nso I'll join you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure.\N- You handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporters, from a newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not allowed visitors now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see their supervising doctor,\NMr. Sekiguchi, for interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to investigate.\NWe'd really like to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't reveal that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Call 110!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police... a patient's turned wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sekiguchi! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the powder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry him to the bed, but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bind his limbs to keep him from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiments for our latest plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Tokyo Poison\NGas Extinction are proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader. Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But General Black... do not\Nunderestimate the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to finish him off before\Nmoving the plan forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Gel Shocker's monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm Inokabuton!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi... prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you see what I can do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton... we'll finish this later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\3c&H727652&\c&H0D0805&}Kabashima Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never seen a poison\Ngas like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to analyze it\Nas fast as we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm afraid there's nothing\Nwe can do before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:44.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,I need to destroy that\Nmonster as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki and Mitsuru sent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they saw the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the forest in Tsukimigaoka."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right alone, Mr. Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be fine. Look after Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to deal with small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Inokabuton?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll face you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life will soon be at an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to disable his nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Things seem to be going\Npoorly for Inokabuton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you expect him\Nto defeat the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given Inokabuton a terrifying weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in addition to his insanity gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton... now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:54.39,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton Horn Gouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like my other weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That wound will never close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be dead soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your final minutes on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, Mitsuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Mr. Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, my blood type is O.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use my blood to save Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Use my blood, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done everything we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to wait\Nfor his will to revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Mr. Taki were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move yet, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still receiving blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton is causing havoc\Nin an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People are collapsing everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton is in an amusement\Npark filled with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here.\NDoctor, please remove the drip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fight now, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! As a doctor, I cannot allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Mr. Tachibana broke\Nquarantine and stole a motorbike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, everyone! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My poison gas has infected\NTachibana's mind, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop it, Pops!\N- Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have reached the limits\Nof what you can do with your blood loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the moment I've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... at last, I'll end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:18.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:26.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.87,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:47.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:01.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:09.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:12.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:16.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:22.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:30.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:45.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:56.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:03.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:06.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:09.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:14.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:17.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... You betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd sell my soul...\Nto a devil like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokabuton Spike-Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyclone Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:02.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's insanity gas plan\Nwas successfully foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:07.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the Kamen Rider would\Ncontinue to face new challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.43,Cont,,0,60,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:13.26,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:12.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:15.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I, General Black,\Nhave sent you Isogin Jaguar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:17.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can you break free of his hellish trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:21.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week will be creator Shotaro Ishimori's\Nfirst time in the director's chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He'll give us speedy action\Nand a strong, awesome Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:30.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We of Gel Shocker hate to admit it, but we do find it amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(397.167,460.389)}Rider in Peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Isogin Jaguar's Hellish Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:50.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:57.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:24:01.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:05.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:08.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.70,0:24:12.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Monstrous Inokabuton, Defeat\NKamen Rider With Insanity Gas
Comment: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider in Peril! Isogin Jaguar's Hellish Trap